---
title: Avocado and Bean Burrito Bowl with Tortilla Dippers and Rice
description: Our Avocado and Bean Burrito Bowl is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R04_W03_UK_V14690-5_Main_4low-ff11aa62.jpg
